videos.description: Dick Vitale is critical of Rex Pflueger not passing the ball, which leads to Jordan Goldwire's steal and layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dicky V. not happy with Pflueger on Goldwire's layup) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Dicky V. not happy with Pflueger on Goldwire's layup

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. gets the ball in the post, then spins by a Notre Dame defender and finishes with a dunk.

videos.description: Zion Williamson is in attendance for Duke's game against Notre Dame after participating in the NBA Rising Stars Game.

videos.description: Duke is showing Notre Dame no mercy and Alex O'Connell's trey gets a smirk out of Zion Williamson in the crowd.

videos.description: Justin Robinson, son of NBA legend David, dunks it down on one end and blocks a shot on the other.
videos.headline: Duke bench goes wild for big sequence by David Robinson's son
